  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GCR - Pyxida family centre 2018</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Families of refugees and migrants in Athens, as well as unaccompanied minors, will continue to receive legal and social support in a space suitable for service delivery and which has grown to a full community centre over 2017.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project record is an extension to the previous Family centre project supported in 2017 &amp; 2018.
This extension will support the running costs of the family day centre as well as a few core staff costs.
This will allow some continuation with the project while activities are being funded from other sources, including the municipality of Athens.</narrative>
  </description>
